Kevin Rahm https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Rahm 0 Kevin Rahm (born January 7, 1971) is an American actor known for his television roles as Kyle McCarty on Judging Amy, Lee McDermott on Desperate Housewives, and Ted Chaough on Mad Men.
